net.proteusframework.core.script

Class ScriptableCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.script.ScriptableCache

  • @Repository(value="scriptableCache")
public class ScriptableCache
extends Object
    Cache for Script related data.

    This is intended to be instantiated by a dependency injection framework and is used internally.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
